models.name: DeepSeek-R1T-Chimera
models.description:
Provided by chutes.ai
DeepSeek-R1T-Chimera merges DeepSeek-R1’s reasoning strengths with DeepSeek-V3 (0324)’s token-efficiency improvements into a MoE Transformer optimized for general text generation. It integrates pretrained weights from both models and is released under the MIT license for research and commercial use.
